{"result": {"folders": ["学习方法"], "nr": 545, "data": {"embed_links": []}, "created": "2015-11-26T09:16:38Z", "bucket_order": 3, "no_answer_followup": 0, "change_log": [{"uid": "ihfyfehjaJQ", "anon": "no", "when": "2015-11-26T09:16:38Z", "data": "ihg10554hzk2fv", "type": "create"}, {"to": "ihg105538lg2fu", "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "anon": "no", "when": "2015-11-26T15:02:41Z", "data": "ihgdd5ntc0058s", "type": "i_answer"}, {"to": "ihg105538lg2fu", "uid": "ihfyfehjaJQ", "anon": "no", "when": "2015-11-27T12:36:35Z", "type": "followup"}, {"to": "ihg105538lg2fu", "uid": "i7e5cw4xLAU", "anon": "no", "when": "2015-11-28T00:35:28Z", "data": "ihid9mky53b1ow", "type": "s_answer"}], "bucket_name": "Today", "history": [{"anon": "no", "uid": "ihfyfehjaJQ", "subject": "非计科&#xff0c;没先修 计算机结构原理", "created": "2015-11-26T09:16:38Z", "content": "<p>    我来自数学系&#xff0c;学过了C语言&#xff0c;数据结构也学得差不多&#xff0c;汇编正在同步学&#xff08;能看懂简单的汇编代码&#xff09;。但是没有学过视频中所说的“计算机结构原理“。之前选修过本校的操作系统课&#xff0c;虽然过了&#xff0c;但实验大部分都没有做&#xff08;当时不会就放弃了。。。&#xff09;&#xff0c;而且学得也不好&#xff0c;所以想重新学一遍。</p>\n<p>    请问这种情况下修这门“操作系统”可以吗&#xff1f;还是必须先修计算机结构原理&#xff1f;</p>"}], "type": "question", "tags": ["student", "学习方法"], "tag_good": [], "unique_views": 287, "children": [{"folders": [], "data": {"embed_links": []}, "children": [], "created": "2015-11-26T15:02:41Z", "bucket_order": 3, "tag_endorse": [{"role": "", "name": "单铭铭", "endorser": {}, "admin": false, "photo": null, "id": "ihfyfehjaJQ", "photo_url": null, "us": false, "facebook_id": null}, {"role": "student", "name": "彭丞杰", "endorser": {}, "admin": false, "photo": null, "id": "iibsg0e1vs3", "photo_url": null, "published": true, "us": false, "facebook_id": null}, {"role": "student", "name": "陈国林", "endorser": {}, "admin": false, "photo": "1456254604_35.png", "id": "ig27bxh3CVK", "photo_url": "https://d1b10bmlvqabco.cloudfront.net/photos/ig27bxh3CVK/1456254604_35.png", "published": true, "us": false, "facebook_id": null}, {"role": "student", "name": "张磊", "endorser": {}, "admin": false, "photo": null, "id": "il1rq3i88qC", "photo_url": null, "published": true, "us": false, "facebook_id": null}], "bucket_name": "Today", "id": "ihgdd5no7ep58r", "history": [{"anon": "no", "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "subject": "", "created": "2015-11-26T15:02:41Z", "content": "<p>这个问题没有确定的答案。下面的观点供参考。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>按正常的学习顺序&#xff0c;操作系统课需要程序设计、汇编语言、数据结构和计算机组成原理这几门的知识作为基础。从这一点上说&#xff0c;建议先完成先修&#xff0c;再来学操作系统是比较系统的。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>换个角度来看&#xff0c;从事计算机相关工作的人中有一些并不是学计算机专业的&#xff0c;其中一些人还做得非常好。于是&#xff0c;我认为只要是对本课程有兴趣的人都可以来学&#xff0c;在学的过程中有缺少的知识&#xff0c;去找相关的知识学就好了。这种做法只适用于自学能力较强&#xff0c;并且带有自己要解决的问题来学操作系统的。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>现在就看你学操作系统课的目的是什么了。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>"}], "type": "i_answer", "tag_endorse_arr": ["ihfyfehjaJQ", "iibsg0e1vs3", "ig27bxh3CVK", "il1rq3i88qC"], "config": {}, "is_tag_endorse": false}, {"anon": "no", "folders": [], "data": {"embed_links": null}, "no_upvotes": 0, "subject": "<p>谢谢向勇老师的指点&#xff0c;虽然兴趣不能代替能力&#xff0c;我还是试着先成为后者。</p>", "created": "2015-11-27T12:36:35Z", "bucket_order": 226, "bucket_name": "Week 11/22 - 11/28", "type": "followup", "tag_good": [], "uid": "ihfyfehjaJQ", "children": [], "tag_good_arr": [], "no_answer": 0, "id": "ihhnl4ufftv5pe", "updated": "2015-11-27T12:36:35Z", "config": {}}, {"folders": [], "data": {"embed_links": []}, "children": [], "created": "2015-11-28T00:35:28Z", "bucket_order": 3, "tag_endorse": [], "bucket_name": "Today", "id": "ihid9mkxkwq1ov", "history": [{"anon": "no", "uid": "i7e5cw4xLAU", "subject": "", "created": "2015-11-28T00:35:28Z", "content": "个人觉得&#xff0c;组成原理没学的话&#xff0c;很多概念还是不好理解的&#xff0c;学习OS会遇到很多困难。当然你会发现学习组成原理的时候也会遇到很多困难&#xff0c;比如需要有数字逻辑课程的知识。所以我觉得学习兴趣很重要的"}], "type": "s_answer", "tag_endorse_arr": [], "config": {}, "is_tag_endorse": false}], "tag_good_arr": [], "no_answer": 0, "id": "ihg105538lg2fu", "config": {}, "status": "active", "drafts": null, "request_instructor": 0, "request_instructor_me": false, "bookmarked": 4, "num_favorites": 1, "my_favorite": false, "is_bookmarked": false, "is_tag_good": fal